data.description: Nicely updated St Charles Mesa home with lots great features as well lots of updated items.  Schedule your showing on this 1/2 acre corner lot property!  The backyard is fully fenced for privacy and security.  The home has a nice open back patio, shed for good storage or to house your farm animals.  The 2 car garage is great for your vehicles or extra storage.  The nice upgrades include: a new roof (2 years old), new flooring throughout.  New paint throughout the interior and exterior, new front door with new front window for a more of an inviting feel.  New water heater (1 year old), updated plumbing, all new light fixtures throughout, new railing gates for the stairwell and a new garage door opener. This front yard is an open pallet to design however you may wish.  In addition, there is potential for a 5th bedroom; however, it's non conforming room but could be a craft room/office, etc.  Call today to schedule a look!  14 month Home Warranty Included!
